# Privacy Policy for Goblin

## About This Policy
Your privacy is important to us. Goblin respects your privacy and complies with applicable laws regarding any personal information we collect—whether through interactions on Discord or via our related websites and services. Personal information includes any data that can identify you, such as your Discord tag, and usage details.

## Information We Collect
- **Voluntarily Provided:** Information you share with us (e.g., via commands or support requests).

## Use of Your Information
We use your information to provide, improve, and secure our services. This includes:
- Operating and enhancing Goblin’s functionality.
- Handling support inquiries.
- Preventing fraud and abuse.
- Sending reminders or updates when needed.

## Data Storage and Security
We store your data globally in secure servers. Although we employ strong security measures to protect your information, no method is 100% secure. You are responsible for safeguarding your credentials.

## Disclosure to Third Parties
We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information only:
- With trusted service providers (e.g., hosting, analytics).
- When legally required (e.g., by law enforcement).
- In the event of a business transfer.

## Your Rights
You have rights regarding your personal information, including:
- **Access & Correction:** Request details of the data we hold and have inaccuracies corrected.
- **Deletion:** Ask us to delete your personal data, subject to legal retention requirements.
- **Consent Withdrawal:** Withdraw consent for non-essential data uses at any time.

## Cookies and Tracking
Goblin uses basic Discord analytics and may use cookies on our websites to enhance your experience. You can control cookies via your browser settings.

## International Transfers
Your data may be processed in jurisdictions with different data protection laws. We ensure that all transfers are made with appropriate safeguards.

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted here and, if significant, communicated to you.

## Contact Us
If you have any concerns or questions about this policy, please contact us at:  
**Discord:** https://discord.gg/XmVkvfWw2t

---

By using Goblin, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
